{"_id":"Tvt87mBULqtrI4Qv","name":"Main Page","permission":{"default":0,"fBZINKCGziZzc3CU":3},"folder":"","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.DRWIQmdqORQdnwzx"}},"content":"<div class=\"contentHeader\">\n<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\">Main Page</h1>\n</div>\n<h2><span id=\"About_Old-School_Essentials\" class=\"mw-headline\">About Old-School Essentials</span></h2>\n<p>Old-School Essentials is an adventure role-playing game of exploration, danger, monsters, and magic. The game is intentionally rules-light, putting the focus of play on imagination, improvisation, and fun. The rules are optimised for ease of use at the table, with meticulous attention to wording and layout clarity. What's more, Old-School Essentials is 100% compatible with the classic Basic/Expert game from 1981, meaning that decades of adventure are at your fingertips!</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Old-School_Essentials_System_Reference_Document\" class=\"mw-headline\">Old-School Essentials System Reference Document</span></h2>\n<p>This online document provides a full reference to the following Old-School Essentials rules modules:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Core Rules</li>\n<li>Classic Fantasy: Genre Rules</li>\n<li>Classic Fantasy: Cleric and Magic-User Spells</li>\n<li>Classic Fantasy: Monsters</li>\n<li>Classic Fantasy: Treasures</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Together, the content of these modules forms a complete rendition of the classic Basic / Expert game.</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Old-School_Essentials_Generators\" class=\"mw-headline\">Old-School Essentials Generators</span></h2>\n<p>Tired of rolling everything by yourself?</p>\n<p>Let the Generators help you! They support:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Treasure</li>\n<li>Encounters</li>\n<li>Spells</li>\n<li>Magic Items</li>\n<li>Retainer</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/generators/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Click here!</a></p>\n<h2><span id=\"Illustrated_PDF_and_Print_Editions\" class=\"mw-headline\">Illustrated PDF and Print Editions</span></h2>\n<p>The complete Old-School Essentials game is available as beautifully illustrated and laid out PDFs and deluxe print books (including a boxed set!) from <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://necroticgnome.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">necroticgnome.com</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://necroticgnome.com/collections/old-school-essentials\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/images/thumb/9/99/Old-School_Essentials_Black_Box_Front_A4_740x.png/300px-Old-School_Essentials_Black_Box_Front_A4_740x.png\" srcset=\"/srd/images/thumb/9/99/Old-School_Essentials_Black_Box_Front_A4_740x.png/450px-Old-School_Essentials_Black_Box_Front_A4_740x.png 1.5x, /srd/images/thumb/9/99/Old-School_Essentials_Black_Box_Front_A4_740x.png/600px-Old-School_Essentials_Black_Box_Front_A4_740x.png 2x\" alt=\"Old-School Essentials Black Box Front A4 740x.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"424\" /></a></p>","img":"icons/svg/book.svg"}
